Pre-Registration Promotion Terms and Conditions – Cubalance Light Pre-registration

Last Updated: 04.05.2026

During the promotion period, eligible users may enter this promotion (“Promotion”) and pre-register to download and install Cubalance Light (the “Game”) on their mobile device via the Google Play Store. By pre-registering for the Game, you agree to be bound by these terms and conditions.

1. Promotion Period
The Promotion period begins on May the 4th 2026 and will expire on the worldwide launch of the Game. Sherlocklini Games (Selina Rust) reserves the right to modify the promotion period, launch date, and reward delivery dates at its sole discretion.

2. The Reward
Users who successfully pre-register for the Game on the Google Play Store will be eligible to receive a one-time pre-registration reward: The Early Bird Skin (the "Reward").

    The Reward is a cosmetic in-game item and does not change a user's performance in the game.

    The Reward has no cash value, is non-transferable, and cannot be traded, sold, or exchanged in any manner.

    The Reward can only be claimed once and is limited to one per Game account.

3. Eligibility & Delivery
To be eligible to participate in the Promotion, you must pre-register for the Game using a valid Google Play account.

    The Reward will be delivered to eligible users upon the worldwide launch of the Game.

    To claim the Reward, users must download and install the Game and log in with the same Google Play account used for pre-registration.

    The Reward will be automatically consumed/unlocked within the Game shortly after initial installation and account verification.

4. Limitations
You cannot claim the pre-registration Reward if any of the following is true:

    Your Google Play account is suspended or found to be in violation of platform terms of service.

    The Game is not supported by your device or is not otherwise available to install in your territory.

    You fail to download and open the Game within [X days/weeks - e.g., 30 days] after the official launch date.

5. General
All decisions related to the Pre-Registration Reward shall be determined solely by Sherlocklini Games (Selina Rust). We reserve the right to substitute the Reward for an item of equal or greater value if necessary and edit the Reward.

